name: ComedyDog
0:
”Alexa, open Comedy Dog.”
”Alexa, ask Comedy Dog to tell me a joke.”
”Alexa, ask Comedy Dog to make me laugh.”

Invocation Name: comedy dog
des: Feeling a little down? Haven't laughed all day? Well, Comedy Dog comes to the rescue. Armed with a large portfolio or hilarious jokes (mostly about dogs), just start up Comedy Dog and get ready to laugh.
